T1  - Stock Market Crashes and the Performance of Circuit Breakers: Empirical Evidence
AU  - LAUTERBACH, BENI
AU  - BEN-ZION, URI
Y1  - 1993/12/01
PY  - 1993
DA  - 1993/12/01
